\mathbb{E}(X) = \sum_{k=1}^{n}n \dbinom{n-1}{k-1} p^k (1-p)^{n-k} = np \left(\sum_{r=0}^{n-1} \dbinom{n-1}{r} p^r (1-p)^{n-1-r} \right) = np
